data.title: Sutherland Cardiology Clinic
data.meta_description: With six hospitals, multiple outpatient and diagnostic centers, and a growing network of physician practices, Methodist Healthcare offers Memphis and the Mid-South the best in healthcare services.
data.text:
Methodist Healthcare-affiliated cardiology clinic

Established in 1972, the board certified physicians at Sutherland Cardiology Clinic are dedicated to our mission of providing excellent clinical, diagnostic, interventional and electrophysiology care.
